Posts.Content: Jan 4, 2018 09:06PM TamaraColo wrote: Definitely started feeling extreme fatigue prior to my diagnosis. My doctor wanted to check for sleep apnea, but when my breast started bleeding, it was all about cancer. I was diagnosed with Stage 1a, and to be honest, I feel like the bleeding (and fatigue) are what led to the early diagnosis.
Posts.Title: Anyone have problems with fatigue prior to diagnosis? cfdr dlj140
